text: Saúl Torres Rojas (born 20 March 1990) is a Bolivian professional footballer who plays for The Strongest as a right back.https://us.soccerway.com/players/saul-torres-rojas/253710/ On 3 March 2019 Torres made his debut for the Bolivia national football team against Nicaragua.https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2019/03/03/world/friendlies/bolivia/nicaragua/2992140/ ==References== ==External links== * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Bolivian footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:Bolivian Primera División players Category:Universitario de Sucre footballers Category:Club Real Potosí players Category:Nacional Potosí players Category:The Strongest players Category:Bolivia international footballers Category:People from Sucre
